
Initial clone
git clone --recursive git@github.com:andmalc/config.git

Git submodule added
git submodule update --init --recursive


stow to copy config files
set full dir path to .ssh to 700


Fish shell
    Set variables
        fish_user_paths /home/andmalc/.local/bin

    pkg manager fisher
        Create submodule for this instead?
        fisher_path /home/andmalc/config/dotfiles/fish/fisher
        curl https://git.io/fisher --create-dirs -sLo ~/.config/fish/fisher/fisher.fish

    pkgs installed
        jethrokuan/fzf
        kennethreitz/fish-pipenv
        oh-my-fish/plugin-bang-bang

