        https://github.com/matchai/spacefish

Tmux
    prefix + I to install tpm modules

Vim
    VundleInstall under Fishshell
        env SHELL=(which sh) vim +BundleInstall! +BundleClean +qall
        https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim/wiki
    Nvim to avoid base16-vim startup errors


Fzf
    https://codeyarns.com/2017/10/24/how-to-install-and-use-fzf/
    Install into shell 
        ./.fzf/install 
        decline keybindings
    Install keybindings package with Fisher.  Said more features than fzf's built in Fish support
        fisher add jethrokuan/fzf
        set -U FZF_LEGACY_KEYBINDINGS 0


